commit.message:
Make-lang.in: Update.

f:
	* Make-lang.in: Update.
	* top.c: Include opts.h. Define cl_options_count and cl_options.
java:
	* Make-lang.in: Update.
	* lang.c: Include opts.h. Define cl_options_count and cl_options.

From-SVN: r67621
